Package com.b2international.snowowl.snomed.api.domain.classification

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IClassificationInput
    Holds required properties for initiating a classification run.
    IClassificationRun
    Reflects the current state of a classification run.
    IEquivalentConcept
    Represents a member of an equivalent concept set.
    IEquivalentConceptSet
    Represents an equivalent concept set, in which all concepts have the same description logic representation, without any extra defining relationships which would differentiate them from each other.
    IRelationshipChange
    Contains a subset of relationship properties which makes it possible to identify an existing redundant relationship for deletion/deactivation, or create a inferred relationship based on it.
    IRelationshipChangeList
    Holds a pageable list of suggested relationship changes.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ChangeNature
    Enumerates possible change types for a particular relationship listed as an IRelationshipChange.
    ClassificationStatus
    Enumerates possible states of a single classification run.
